import React from 'react'
import LeftSidebar from './LeftSidebar'
import Mainbar from './Mainbar'
import RightSidebar from './RightSidebar'
import { Container, Wrapper } from './styles/Dashboard.styled'

const Dashboard = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Wrapper>
        <LeftSidebar />
        <Mainbar text="201816427" />
        <RightSidebar />
      </Wrapper>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Dashboard
